{
  "stem": "4361.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With the SS, with the dog, with the truncheons hitting, and we walked-- there was a big road separating the men's [INAUDIBLE]-- the man's camps from the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the men would come, and they would see women go through the road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would come close to the wire-- not too close, because the wire, as you know, were electrified-- and would yell out names.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the women would yell back, yes, she's here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we would ask for names, and whoever was caught, the SS would hit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was done anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I kept asking for my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I kept asking for my father, because I thought that he made it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kept asking for my brother, my older brother, because my Alex I knew was somewhere in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never got any information.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in the [NON-ENGLISH] until about November.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what I remember, and I would like to tell that story of Yom Kippur in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was Yom Kippur in Auschwitz, because word got around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody was keeping some count, and word got around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night in that particular block, as I'm sure in all the other blocks, women were singing the And next morning, we went out for [NON-ENGLISH] appell.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought coffee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody touched it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no communication, but it just so happened they took us to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I say they, I mean the SS, and we did the required quota, or we didn't make the required quota, because it was impossible anyway.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
